      "properties": {},
      "widgets_values": [
        "AnyVoice：一個模板，三種來源 → 聲音複製\n\nDefault path: YouTube. Paste a URL, tick consent, then Queue.\nAudio file path: connect Load Audio, tick consent on AnyVoice Reference From Audio, set \"Use uploaded audio\" switch to true.\nRecording path: record with Record Audio, keep/edit the exact transcript, tick consent, set \"Use recording\" switch to true.\n\nSwitch rules: Use recording overrides uploaded/YouTube. If Use recording is false, Use uploaded audio chooses uploaded audio; otherwise YouTube runs. The switches are lazy, so only the selected source is evaluated.\n\nRequires yt-dlp + ffmpeg, the shared VoxCPM Python env, and optionally the hot worker on :8765 for fast synthesis."
      ],
      "color": "#432",
      "bgcolor": "#653"
    },
